{"tid":2184091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陪審員上周發現彥霖遺物有青協單張 警上周到附近青協調查 惟去年閉路電視紀錄已刪除","createTime":"2020-09-01T10:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T14:49:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1d8003c6a71e7e8d8c3f3b90e3e324d28e632e","tid":2184091,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:28:54.000Z","msg":"參與反送中集會的15歲職訓局青年書院女生陳彥霖，去年9月底離奇赤裸浮屍海面，警方及後指死因無可疑。死因庭今繼續研訊，上周五有陪審員發現，彥霖失蹤前遺留在知專的失物中，有一份寫有「唔好貪得意、大麻咪亂試」 的青協宣傳單張，單張顯示機構位於日出康城第一期首都；陪審員懷疑彥霖當晚乘的士於緻藍天下車後，曾走至鄰近的青協。但警員李豪傑當時指不清楚有關資訊，故未有循此方向調查。研訊主任今午重新傳召警員出庭作供。<br />\n<br />\n警方又問到，青協有否保存去年9月19日、即彥霖疑乘的士去緻藍天當日的閉路電視紀錄，但青協稱有關紀錄僅會保存一個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/ZEGN74E3RJBH5E5LMEV6JDIDTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FZEGN74E3RJBH5E5LMEV6JDIDTE%2F&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYbY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=58437c49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200901%2FZEGN74E3RJBH5E5LMEV6JDIDTE%2F&h=6c11029d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200901/ZEGN74E3RJBH5E5LMEV6JDIDTE/</a>"},{"pid":"49abe56c9e9f6b96b381765b4f02c4a8cdde6a61","tid":2184091,"uid":119607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:29:48.000Z","msg":"黨媒truth hk又出fake news 又用721微博假圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2183510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2183510</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bad8c7642c7a329d99b4d85798e360c2a4916f75","tid":2184091,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49abe56c9e9f6b96b381765b4f02c4a8cdde6a61","tid":2184091,"uid":119607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:29:48.000Z","msg":"黨媒truth hk又出fake news 又用721微博假圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2183510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2183510</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T